--- !u!114 &3100007
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 3100001}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 2ea6422d1962ba3409655b2a2dc99dff, type: 3}
  m_Name:
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::Mossmark.Prototype4.AcquaintableAttendable
  entityId: p4_smokehouse
  unfamiliarShortName: A low building
  unfamiliarDescription: A low building, shut up tight, its walls dark with weather
    or with work. Hard to say which, from the path.
  unfamiliarTint: {r: 0.45, g: 0.45, b: 0.45, a: 1}
  unfamiliarInteractionLine: Hold E to look the place over
  seededPropertyIds:
  - burns_slow
  seededKnowledgeLead: The place is given to
  trueStateNote: re-raised after the flood on its own old timbers; fired every autumn
    run; racks hung ready
  acquaintanceStages:
  - stageId: acquainted
    stageDisplayName: Acquainted
    attendsCost: 2
    shortName: A smokehouse
    description: A smokehouse. The dark on the walls is soot, not rot, and the roof
      is sound. Kept, though it has not been fired in a while.
    tint: {r: 0.55, g: 0.5, b: 0.42, a: 1}
    interactionLine: Hold E to take the measure of it
    attendFlavors:
    - Under the eaves the smell of old smoke holds on, faint but certain.
  - stageId: known
    stageDisplayName: Known
    attendsCost: 3
    shortName: The Smokehouse
    description: The smokehouse, re-raised on its own old timbers after the river
      took the walls. Fired every autumn run for longer than anyone here remembers,
      and the eaves are hung ready for this one.
    tint: {r: 0.72, g: 0.45, b: 0.3, a: 1}
    interactionLine: Hold E to stand a while inside
    attendFlavors:
    - The racks are worn smooth where a hundred seasons of eels have hung.
    - The light comes through the smoke-hole the way it was built to, thin and exactly
      placed.
  attendDuration: 2
  unfamiliarAttendFlavors:
  - You walk its walls. Shut up, quiet, keeping its own counsel.
