--- !u!114 &3500007
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 3500001}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 2ea6422d1962ba3409655b2a2dc99dff, type: 3}
  m_Name:
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::Mossmark.Prototype4.AcquaintableAttendable
  entityId: p4_collier
  unfamiliarShortName: A grey figure
  unfamiliarDescription: A figure grey to the elbows, minding something on the slope
    you can't see from here. They don't turn around.
  unfamiliarTint: {r: 0.45, g: 0.45, b: 0.45, a: 1}
  unfamiliarInteractionLine: Hold E to watch a while
  seededPropertyIds:
  - burns_slow
  seededKnowledgeLead: They speak of
  trueStateNote: burns the hearth ring alone since their partner died; sleeps beside
    lit clamps; counts burns in nights
  acquaintanceStages:
  - stageId: acquainted
    stageDisplayName: Acquainted
    attendsCost: 2
    shortName: A charcoal-burner
    description: A charcoal-burner. The grey is ash, and the not-turning-around is
      the work. A burn left alone will eat itself.
    tint: {r: 0.5, g: 0.48, b: 0.52, a: 1}
    interactionLine: Hold E to keep watch alongside them
    attendFlavors:
    - They crouch and listen to the clamp like a doctor at a chest, then shift one
      turf a hand's width.
  - stageId: known
    stageDisplayName: Known
    attendsCost: 3
    shortName: The Collier
    description: The collier, who sleeps beside the clamp when it's lit and counts
      the burn in nights, not days. There were two of them once. The second bed
      in the bothy has been cold a year.
    tint: {r: 0.38, g: 0.36, b: 0.45, a: 1}
    interactionLine: Hold E to share the watch
    attendFlavors:
    - They bank the fire with turves and sit back on their heels. Nothing to do
      now, and everything to mind.
    - Once, without a word, they point. A thin blue thread of smoke, running true.
  attendDuration: 2
  unfamiliarAttendFlavors:
  - You watch the grey figure work. Whatever it tends, it tends it like a vigil.
