--- !u!114 &3600007
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 3600001}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 2ea6422d1962ba3409655b2a2dc99dff, type: 3}
  m_Name:
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::Mossmark.Prototype4.AcquaintableAttendable
  entityId: p4_bothy
  unfamiliarShortName: A squat shelter
  unfamiliarDescription: A squat shelter, turf-roofed, built against weather rather
    than for comfort. No smoke from it now.
  unfamiliarTint: {r: 0.45, g: 0.45, b: 0.45, a: 1}
  unfamiliarInteractionLine: Hold E to look the place over
  seededPropertyIds:
  - keeps_well
  seededKnowledgeLead: The place holds to
  trueStateNote: raised by two colliers the year the ring was recut; kept by one;
    the second bed a year cold
  acquaintanceStages:
  - stageId: acquainted
    stageDisplayName: Acquainted
    attendsCost: 2
    shortName: A bothy
    description: A working bothy. Someone sleeps here in the burning seasons, close
      to whatever the work is. One bed slept in, by the wear of the door path.
    tint: {r: 0.5, g: 0.47, b: 0.4, a: 1}
    interactionLine: Hold E to take the measure of it
    attendFlavors:
    - The turf roof is patched in years. Darker squares, lighter squares, a calendar
      of mendings.
  - stageId: known
    stageDisplayName: Known
    attendsCost: 3
    shortName: The Colliers' Bothy
    description: The colliers' bothy, two beds and one slept in. The pair of them
      raised it the year the hearth ring was recut, and one of them has mended it
      alone every spring since.
    tint: {r: 0.62, g: 0.5, b: 0.35, a: 1}
    interactionLine: Hold E to sit in the doorway
    attendFlavors:
    - Two cups on the shelf. One is dusty, and has not been moved, and will not
      be.
  attendDuration: 2
  unfamiliarAttendFlavors:
  - You circle the shelter. Built low, built stubborn. It gives nothing away.
