--- !u!114 &3700007
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 3700001}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 2ea6422d1962ba3409655b2a2dc99dff, type: 3}
  m_Name:
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::Mossmark.Prototype4.AcquaintableAttendable
  entityId: p4_hearth_ring
  unfamiliarShortName: A bare circle
  unfamiliarDescription: A circle of ground where nothing grows, dark under the leaf-fall.
    Old, whatever it is.
  unfamiliarTint: {r: 0.45, g: 0.45, b: 0.45, a: 1}
  unfamiliarInteractionLine: Hold E to walk the ground
  seededPropertyIds:
  - burns_slow
  seededKnowledgeLead: The ground here is given to
  trueStateNote: cut generations back for the clean updraught; a hundred burns deep
    in char; paces the coppice around it
  acquaintanceStages:
  - stageId: acquainted
    stageDisplayName: Acquainted
    attendsCost: 2
    shortName: A burn site
    description: A burn site. A hearth ring, used and used again. Kick the leaf-fall
      aside and the char goes down past a finger's depth.
    tint: {r: 0.45, g: 0.4, b: 0.38, a: 1}
    interactionLine: Hold E to walk the ring
    attendFlavors:
    - After rain the ground gives back a heat-smell, like an old promise.
  - stageId: known
    stageDisplayName: Known
    attendsCost: 3
    shortName: The Hearth Ring
    description: The hearth ring, cut generations back where the draught runs clean
      up the slope. Char this deep is a hundred burns, and the coppice all around
      is the age it is because of this circle.
    tint: {r: 0.35, g: 0.3, b: 0.3, a: 1}
    interactionLine: Hold E to stand in the circle
    attendFlavors:
    - From the ring's center the coppice reads in rings of its own. This year's
      growth, last year's, the years before.
    - Charcoal glints in the black like something sorted, not spilled.
  attendDuration: 2
  unfamiliarAttendFlavors:
  - You toe the dark ground. It is not mud and it is not shadow.
